    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once you reach 14th level, you gain the ability to infect a humanoid's mind with the alien magic of your patron. You can use your action to touch an incapacitated humanoid. That creature is then charmed by you until a @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.vcL7CJzvhhPeIObK]{Remove Curse} spell is cast on it, the charmed condition is removed from it, or you use this feature again. If the charm is removed you instantaneously know.</p><p>You can communicate telepathically with the charmed creature as long as the two of you are on the same plane of existence.</p>",
